I18N.Title: WAF
I18N.Translation: The 'Official audio file webpage' frame is a URL pointing at a file specific webpage.

I18N.Title: WAR
I18N.Translation: The 'Official artist/performer webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the artists official webpage. There may be more than one "WAR" frame in a tag if the audio contains more than one performer.

I18N.Title: WAS
I18N.Translation: The 'Official audio source webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the official webpage for the source of the audio file, e.g. a movie.

I18N.Title: WCM
I18N.Translation: The 'Commercial information' frame is a URL pointing at a webpage with information such as where the album can be bought. There may be more than one "WCM" frame in a tag.

I18N.Title: WCP
I18N.Translation: The 'Copyright/Legal information' frame is a URL pointing at a webpage where the terms of use and ownership of the file is described.

I18N.Title: WPB
I18N.Translation: The 'Publishers official webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the official wepage for the publisher.
